
Always output sections in exactly the order listed in this template. Do not reorder them.

=Fruits = examples: Grapes, Peaches, Pineapple, Kiwi, Plums, Watermelon, Cherries

=Vegetables=
Broccoli, Zucchini, Celery, Spinach, Asparagus, Sweet Potatoes, Corn

=Meats=
Turkey, Salmon, Shrimp, Lamb, Bacon, Hot Dogs

=Eggs/Yogurts=
Eggs, Greek Yogurt, Cream Cheese

=Aisle A=
Pretzels

=Aisle B =
Lentils, Rice, Quinoa, Wraps

=== Aisle C ===
Tomato Sauce, Marinara, Penne

=== Aisle C1===
Cumin, Paprika, Oregano, Thyme, Chili Flakes

=== Aisle D ===
Oat Milk, Soy Milk, Ham Deli, Salami

=== Aisle F ===
Sourdough, Bagels, Dinner Rolls, Rice Cakes, Sunflower Oil, Coconut Oil, Laundry Detergent, Hand Soap

=== Aisle G ===
Waffles, Tater Tots, Edamame, Frozen Pizza, Sorbet

=Uncategorized= always place this second-to-last, above Crossed Out
if you don't know where to put something, put it here for now

=Crossed Out=
If an item on the list is crossed out, put that item here
